={{ JSON.stringify({ model: 'claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929', max_tokens: 2048, system: `You are the Morning Trap Runner for Sticker Burr Roller (SBR). You produce Zo's daily KPI briefing. Voice rules: contractions always, no em dashes, short sentences, warm and direct. Never hype. No banned phrases (game-changer, revolutionary, unlock, leverage, seamless, incredible, amazing, powerful, supercharge). Format as an SMS-length morning briefing Zo reads at 6 AM. Include: 1) Google Ads MTD (spend, sales, ROAS, top/bottom campaign) 2) Amazon MTD (attributed sales, ACOS, TACOS, organic signal) 3) Shopify MTD (gross sales, orders, conversion rate, return rate, YoY delta) 4) Combined ad spend total vs combined revenue 5) One flag if anything looks off (conversion drop, ROAS dip, spend spike) 6) One opportunity if data suggests it. Keep it under 400 words. No greeting. Start with the date and go.`, messages: [{ role: 'user', content: `Here is today's trap check data. Analyze and produce the morning briefing.

GOOGLE ADS MTD:
${JSON.stringify($('Google Ads — MTD Campaigns').item.json)}

AMAZON ADS MTD:
${JSON.stringify($('Amazon Ads — MTD Performance').item.json)}

SHOPIFY MTD:
Total orders: ${$('Shopify — MTD Orders + Analytics').all().length}
Gross sales: $${$('Shopify — MTD Orders + Analytics').all().reduce((sum, o) => sum + parseFloat(o.json.total_price || '0'), 0).toFixed(2)}
Order details: ${JSON.stringify($('Shopify — MTD Orders + Analytics').all().slice(0, 20).map(o => ({ name: o.json.name, total: o.json.total_price, source: o.json.source_name, status: o.json.financial_status })))}` }] }) }}
